Simple. [list]
[*][color=#3c78d8]No ENB,[/color]

[*][size=5]#NoFilter[/size]
[/list]I wanted to show you, that using almost only Racemenu tools, it's possible to make quite interesting faces.(and of course to avoid post/comments like - "my character don't look like in picture" xd)

Okay.  
[color=#00ff00]Required[/color] mods are known to all
RaceMenu
Ks Hairdos Renewal
The Eyes of Beauty
Apachii SkyHair
I also recommend to use [url=https://www.vectorplexus.com/]Shape Atlas for Men[/url]﻿ (with other bodies should be fine, but it may be necessary to rescale head), and face textures from ﻿﻿Geonox mod
File contains my facial hair texture. That's all.
Enjoy :D
